Headings (for hierarchy and impact)
H1 (Main title): 2.5rem – 3rem
H2 (Section titles): 2rem – 2.5rem
H3 (Subtitles): 1.5rem – 2rem
H4 (Smaller section headers): 1.25rem – 1.5rem
Body Text (for readability)
Paragraphs (default text): 1rem – 1.125rem
Secondary text (less important info): 0.875rem – 1rem
Captions & footnotes: 0.75rem – 0.875rem
Navigation & Buttons (for accessibility)
Navbar links: 1rem – 1.125rem
Buttons (standard size): 1rem – 1.25rem
Small buttons or tags: 0.875rem
Code or Monospace Text (if needed)
Inline code snippets: 0.875rem – 1rem
Code blocks: 1rem – 1.125rem
Base font-size 16px